title: Mass File Creation IRT LockBit 3.0 
id: 1bf34273-75c8-46bf-99ce-3f3fb6be4688
description: Detects when more than 25 files are created with a .HLJkNskOq file extension within a 10 second window, indicative of LockBit 3.0 Ransomware.
status: experimental
references:
    - https://www.trendmicro.com/en_th/research/22/g/lockbit-ransomware-group-augments-its-latest-variant--lockbit-3-.html
author: Tyler Casey @1qazCasey, @scythe_io
date: 2024/01/16
tags:
  - attack.TA0040
  - attack.T1486
logsource:
    category: windows
    product: sysmon
detection:
    selection:
     EventID: 11
     TargetFilename|endswith:
      - '.HLJkNskOq'
    timeframe: 10s
    condition: selection | count() by TargetFilename > 25
falsepositives:
    - Legitimate software creating files with same extension as LockBit 3.0 Ransomware.
level: high
